OL,3,C'I was petrified... it was blind
OL,4,Crage': Man's life changed after
OL,5,Cpartner's abuse
OL,7,FBarry said: "I had become so so ill. I
OL,8,Fhad lost three stone in weight. I
OL,9,Fbecame very isolated and vacant.
OL,10,FIsolated from people.
OL,12,F"I was having to have conversations on
OL,13,Fthe phone in a whisper mode. I felt
OL,14,Ftrapped".
OL,16,FOn 30 January 2024, the 45-year-old
OL,17,Fwas attacked at home.
OL,19,FHe feared for his life when his
OL,20,Fpartner grabbed him and bit him.
