OL,3,C'I was petrified... it was blind
OL,4,Crage': Man's life changed after
OL,5,Cpartner's abuse
OL,7,F"I was petrified. It was like a blind
OL,8,Frage. The aggression was unbelievable.
OL,9,FWhen he caught me and wouldn't let me
OL,10,Fgo and he bit me I just thought this
OL,11,Fis not the person I met," Barry said.
OL,13,FHis former boyfriend was charged with
OL,14,Fcommon assault with domestic abuse as
OL,15,Fan aggravating factor.
OL,17,FThe 32-year-old was convicted at
OL,18,FLisburn Magistrates' Court in November
OL,19,F2024 and sentenced to five months in
OL,20,Fprison, suspended for two years.
