OL,3,C'I was petrified... it was blind
OL,4,Crage': Man's life changed after
OL,5,Cpartner's abuse
OL,7,F"I was very lucky to get it through
OL,8,Fthe courts with the strength I didn't
OL,9,Frealise I had. And to get the
OL,10,Fconviction meant more to me than
OL,11,Fanything else.
OL,13,F"For men that think this doesn't
OL,14,Fhappen to other men, yes it does.
OL,15,FNobody should be afraid to speak out.
OL,16,FFind yourself someone you can confide
OL,17,Fin. Find yourself a safe space. That's
OL,18,Fthe most important thing".
